    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Through long and intensive training you mastered Poise. Few people in this world can match your capabilities in this area.</p><p>Gain the following master feats: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.80AC6Q1m0eQiE7Et]{Tumbling Theft}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.gBSPbQRXdagZTUwY]{Kip Up}.</p><p><strong>Skill Potency</strong></p><p>At 9th level, you gain a +2 item bonus to Acrobatics checks involving @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.kMcV8e5EZUxa6evt]{Squeeze}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.M76ycLAqHoAgbcej]{Balance}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.21WIfSu7Xd7uKqV8]{Tumble Through}. At 17th level, this bonus increases to +3.</p>",
